longBusinessSummary: Hotel Chocolat Group plc manufactures, sells, and retails chocolates under the Hotel Chocolat brand name in the United Kingdom, rest of Europe, and internationally. It offers a range of chocolates, including gift, and rare and vintage chocolates, as well as related drinks, alcohols, and beauty products. The company sells its products through a network of stores, as well as through online subscription; and operates restaurants, hotels, and cocoa estates. It also holds properties. The company operates 127 Hotel Chocolat locations in the United Kingdom and Ireland; and 4 in the United States. Hotel Chocolat Group plc was founded in 1993 and is headquartered in Royston, the United Kingdom.
